QuestData.Title: The Push Westward
QuestData.Description: Our work is done here, $n. Against all odds, we stopped the Neferset advance on Nahom.$B$BLet us join the forces pushing west, lest they take all the glory for themselves.$B$BThey must've reached the outskirts of Neferset City by now.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to King Phaoris at the Neferset City Outskirts in Uldum.
